                <h1>Instant <span>Gardens</span></h1>
                <p class="tagline">"Plants for People"</p>
                <div class="about">
                    <p>Welcome to Instant Gardens, your trusted source for beautiful, easy-to-grow grass that quickly turns any space into a lush, vibrant green oasis.</p>
                    <p>Located at the serene Sigwaca Farm Lodge in Dwaleni, Eswatini, we specialize in premium grass seedlings perfect for transforming yards, homes, offices, balconies, and gardens. Our high-quality plugs are simple to install and establish rapidly, creating a thick, durable lawn that can handle heavy foot traffic and tough weather conditions. Whether you're in a sunny or shaded region, we help you choose the ideal grass variety suited to Eswatini's climate.</p>
                    <p>We offer our strong, healthy seedlings in convenient trays of 200 each, with a minimum order of just one tray to make it easy for everyone to start their green journey. <strong>Important Note: We sell seedlings only – no seeds or mature turf.</strong> At Instant Gardens, we bring nature closer to you with premium instant lawns and grasses that are easy to grow and maintain. Grow easy. Grow green. Grow happy!</p>
                </div>
            </div>
